    'description' => 'Poll an RSS/Atom feed, diff against the last snapshot stored in SQLite, and return only what is NEW since the last run. Persists state (item GUIDs, titles, timestamps) in a SQLite database so it works across sessions. Uses http_fetch + SimpleXML internally. Great for monitoring news, releases, blog posts. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
